<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 18:10:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>如果以色列和哈马斯不达成协议，加沙战斗将漫无目的地拖延，北部可能陷入全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/without-israel-hamas-deal-gaza-fighting-will-drag-on-as-north-may-plunge-into-all-out-war/00000190-0d69-d0f9-a1d5-dd6940190000</link><description>辛瓦尔的结束战争要求是内塔尼亚胡无意满足的，这让拜登政府不知所措 ■ 以色列在没有明确战略的情况下加大针对真主党高级领导人的打击力度，纳斯鲁拉则升级报复性袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:46:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/without-israel-hamas-deal-gaza-fighting-will-drag-on-as-north-may-plunge-into-all-out-war/00000190-0d69-d0f9-a1d5-dd6940190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，边境敌对行动达到顶峰时，真主党向以色列北部发射了 200 多枚火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/idf-says-hezbollah-fired-over-200-rockets-at-israels-north-as-border-hostilities-peak/00000190-0ca4-dfa9-a9fc-cff52fe00000</link><description>这次大规模袭击是在真主党在冲突中伤亡最高的人员被杀之后发生的。以色列国防军官员表示，以色列尚未决定对黎巴嫩进行大规模军事反应</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/idf-says-hezbollah-fired-over-200-rockets-at-israels-north-as-border-hostilities-peak/00000190-0ca4-dfa9-a9fc-cff52fe00000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯要求以色列在休战一周内从加沙撤军，并首先释放人质尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/hamas-responds-to-egypt-qatar-on-gaza-cease-fire-and-hostage-release-plan/00000190-08db-d0f9-a1d5-d8fb2b450000</link><description>哈马斯消息人士告诉《国土报》，此举“旨在确保以色列无法逃避协议的所有阶段，并在所有人质获释后重新投入战斗。”以色列称哈马斯的回应等于拒绝该提议本身</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">ht