3a5cd50000</guid></item><item><title>《华尔街日报》：哈马斯绑架者将获救的人质锁在浴室里，威胁要杀死他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/wsj-hamas-captors-locked-rescued-hostages-in-bathroom-threatened-to-kill-them/00000190-0b96-dbe3-a1da-1bb7d7ef0000</link><description>《华尔街日报》称，有关周六获救的三名以色列人质被俘的新细节是基于对他们的亲属以及以色列安全和医疗官员的采访</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 09:35:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/wsj-hamas-captors-locked-rescued-hostages-in-bathroom-threatened-to-kill-them/00000190-0b96-dbe3-a1da-1bb7d7ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩的空袭杀死了战争开始以来目标的“最高级”真主党指挥官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/israeli-strike-in-lebanon-kills-most-senior-hezbollah-commander-targeted-since-war-began/00000190-0b56-db28-a995-4fdf34940000</link><description>三名真主党战士也在针对高级战地指挥官塔勒布·阿卜杜拉（又名阿布·塔勒布）的袭击中丧生</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 08:00:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/israeli-strike-in-lebanon-kills-most-senior-hezbollah-commander-targeted-since-war-began/00000190-0b56-db28-a995-4fdf34940000</guid></item><item><title>联合国新报告指责以色列和哈马斯犯有反人类罪和战争罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/new-un-report-accuses-israel-and-hamas-of-crimes-against-humanity-and-war-crimes/00000190-0992-d067-adb0-8fb658b70000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府可能会攻击该报告及其主要作者——曾被指控反犹太主义的南非法学家</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 06:56:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/new-un-report-accuses-israel-and-hamas-of-crimes-against-humanity-and-war-crimes/00000190-0992-d067-adb0-8fb658b70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军杀死黎巴嫩高级指挥官后，真主党向以色列北部发射了数百枚火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article-live/israeli-official-hamas-has-rejected-bidens-gaza-cease-fire-proposal/00000190-0a43-dd57-abb4-7a4b7dc20000