emption-likud-lawmakers-call-to-fire-gallant/00000190-083b-d067-adb0-8e3fd2350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 249 天：美国高级官员表示，哈马斯在战后无法统治加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-249-hamas-cannot-rule-gaza-after-war-top-u-s-official-says/00000190-0829-d667-abf0-6ceb14f90000</link><description>哈马斯表示接受美国起草的联合国安理会决议，要求停火并释放所有人质，并准备就其细节进行谈判 ■ 美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文表示，哈马斯在战后无法继续在加沙掌权 ■ 发射了 50 枚火箭来自黎巴嫩的戈兰高地 ■ 以色列北部城市海法自 1 月以来首次响起火箭警报 ■ 战争进入 249 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 16:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-249-hamas-cannot-rule-gaza-after-war-top-u-s-official-says/00000190-0829-d667-abf0-6ceb14f90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡谈论了一场对抗伊朗核武器的精彩比赛——仅此而已</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-talks-a-good-game-against-iranian-nukes-and-thats-it/00000190-06ff-d5ad-ad93-26ff98a10000</link><description>以色列总理从未制定过一致的政策来对抗伊朗核计划，包括2018年他让特朗普退出核协议时。内塔尼亚胡在国会的演讲中，预计会有更多诸如“西方正面临毁灭”之类的咆哮</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 16:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-talks-a-good-game-against-iranian-nukes-and-thats-it/00000190-06ff-d5ad-ad93-26ff98a10000</guid></item><item><title>皮尤调查显示，随着加沙战争的拖延，拜登在以色列人中的支持率下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/bidens-popularity-among-israelis-drops-as-gaza-war-drags-on-pew-survey-shows/00000190-075f-d0f9-a1d5-d77f6cd90000</link><description>对美国总统的信心从 68% 下降至 57%，仅领先特朗普 3 个百分点</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 15:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/bidens-popularity-among-israelis-drops-as-gaza-war-drags-on-pew-survey-shows/00000190-075f-d0f9-a1d5-d77f6cd90000</guid></item><item><title>包括哈马斯成员在内的四名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列